<p>List every service individually with descriptions.</p>
<ul>
<li>Traditional funeral services</li>
<li>Cremation services (direct and with ceremony)</li>
<li>Pre-planning and pre-arrangement services</li>
<li>Memorial services and celebrations of life</li>
<li>Graveside services</li>
<li>Military and veteran funeral honors</li>
